[mypy-boto3-builder](https://github.com/youtype/mypy_boto3_builder) carefully generates type annotations for each service, patiently waiting for `aiobotocore` updates. It delivers a drop-in type annotations for you and makes sure that: - All available `aiobotocore` services are covered. - Each public class and method of every `aiobotocore` service gets valid type annotations extracted from the documentation (blame `botocore` docs if types are incorrect). -
